{"tid":1320448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地咁樣做，咩搞到警察唔想番工law﹗你地知唔知架﹗","createTime":"2019-07-15T11:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:48:52.000Z","uid":113124,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62e869081a40ed648a6ab21d1004478039bd8a3e","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"各位，廢話少說，警隊已是林鄭政權最後一張牌，只要失去作用，特首眾叛親離。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">這是大家都不想看到的，對不﹖</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n首先，大部份警察如一般市民一樣，番工是核心價值，而今日有警方員佐級組織割蓆，好簡單，好易理解。大家要諗下自己炒老細魷魚既時候多數發生左咩事。例如同事磨擦，老細長期苛待，低人工，環境不佳等等。我地只要降低警員的工作滿意及滿足感便可以。當情緒爆發，警員自然PEA住番工，成為扮工男女。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">所以請遊行人士不要﹗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 令警員工作環境變得更差<br />\n示威者戰術愈好，裝備愈佳，均令警員任務完成難度提升。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">頻常的社會運動亦令警員要無時無刻要OT工作，執法過程又容易受傷</span></strong>，呢份工實在唔抵做﹗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">所以請文宣組不要再強調﹕</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 強調無良上司苛待<br />\n錯誤戰術，圍堵攬炒，高官一哥貓哭老鼠。前線警員完全係CONDOM，用完即棄，更加要打到死才心息，成為政治棋上被吃的卒，實在唔值得賣命。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任何事故後，警員最不想看到的是﹕上級錯誤運用戰術求邀功，前線手捉賤如泥。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">請任何人也不要(市民、任何網民)</span></strong><br />\n3. 抹黑警方形象<br />\n行動驅散，比傳媒吊。唔行動企係度，示威者吊。唔做野，老細吊。入區又比市民吊。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警員日日比人問老母，呢份工真係好撚慘，請大家唔見到警察就大聲狂吊，仲要吊唔停﹗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察係打份工，如果大家都比咁大壓力比警方，佢地就真係好慘，最後番到唔想番，呢點大家都唔想架，係咪﹖</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b21023274e66f89d88abd652d1c65b51cc16f1f6","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb4f164337578cbea13d530ff960a8904cfdea","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0d602187d0cefa56e62ffd279aa7151e900e5e","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2474d5416adae752528d9c969fd1a3c809956f","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a486877c53bdb1b4c54921b08eddcefbba4f0","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20de2a7c77688f2bcb8a5e4ee5e4be05774faa1c","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25a8c8d06039bfe52c9a9ed8bedfbf84937bb38","tid":1320448,"uid":169074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97b3aeec2f54df18059208492df27bf1312f3e99","tid":1320448,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:38:46.000Z","msg":"港共期待緊死第一個警察或者示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1318968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1318968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a8a6feb26597158b502d08918bc63b5d154fdcd","tid":1320448,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f75748aff620c2a336d0ec131338aed9b6dc502","tid":1320448,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:39:36.000Z","msg":"唔好咁做啦，佢地好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif